data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, NO FAULT OF THE SELLERS. PRICE REDUCTION! MOTIVATED SELLERS.  Welcome home! This home has 3 bedrooms on the main level, 4th nonconforming in the walkout basement. Fireplace in the living room and in the finished basement.  Hardwoods in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances. Living room also has hardwoods.   Carpet in the bedrooms.  Tile in the family room in the basement.  Laundry room is in the basement, sump pump, new roof.  Large backyard with storage shed.  Sunroom off of the 2nd bedroom.   $3,000 carpet allowance for the bedrooms.  Make this home your own!
